---
import EventLayout from "../../components/EventLayout.astro";

const images = [
  { src: "/ai-hackathon-ii/4.jpg", alt: "AI Hackathon II" },
  { src: "/ai-hackathon-ii/1.jpg", alt: "AI Hackathon II" },
  { src: "/ai-hackathon-ii/3.jpg", alt: "AI Hackathon II" },
  { src: "/ai-hackathon-ii/2.jpg", alt: "AI Hackathon II" },
];
---

<EventLayout
  title="AI Hackathon II"
  date="May 10, 2025"
  location="The Beacon, Antwerp"
  type="Hackathon"
  description="Augmenting Antwerp with AI - teams built location-aware apps that bridge the digital and physical worlds."
  images={images}
>
  <p>The second hackathon challenged teams to augment Antwerp with intelligent, location-aware applications. From gamified city exploration to AI-powered tour guides, the solutions showed what happens when you point builders at a city-scale problem.</p>
  <p>Winners included a Pokemon Go-style Antwerp explorer, a smart city companion called DayByDay, and an AI tour guide narrated by Tom Waes. We also successfully depleted the pizza supply - a reliable measure of attendance.</p>
  <p>Made possible by sponsors <strong>Dashdot</strong> and <strong>Rollo</strong>, and the organizing efforts of Filip, Oleksandr, Thibaud, Wim, Nathan, Robin, and <strong>The Beacon</strong>.</p>
</EventLayout>
